Elsie Leslie https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsie_Leslie 0 Elsie Leslie (August 14, 1881 – October 31, 1966) was an American actress. She was America's first child star and the highest paid and most popular child actress of her era. Elsie_Leslie ( August_14_,_1881 – October_31_,_1966 ) was an_American_actress .
